comments.text:
I know these after market duel screen handhelds are dope…. but I don’t get it. Here’s my reasons
1) Can’t do 3D. I know some people don’t like the 3D feature but it’s actually pretty dope for a lot of games.
2) The second screen makes no fucking sense for most emulation. I mean, it doesn’t so…
3) Legit hardware isn’t that expensive, is endlessly mod-able, and can play generations of games natively

Just buy a New 3DS XL. Yeah, they’ve gone up in price but they’re still cheaper than these stupid Android devices. Also, Android sucks and should be avoided at all cost. If a device doesn’t let you side load Linux, it sucks.
